<item>
            <title>[LU-4955] Reset non-specified LFSCK parameters when the LFSCK is reset</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4955</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;To make the semantics more clear, when &quot;--reset&quot; or &quot;-r&quot; is specified when start the LFSCK manually, then all the non-specified parameters will be set as default values.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If the former LFSCK instance has already completed, then when re-trigger the LFSCK, it will restart from the beginning, and all the non-specified parameters will be set as default values.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
